name: extreme_combo_if_do_with_comparison_roundtrip
section: feature-interactions-deep
args: cond:Bool setup:Int a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Mixed helpers, direct dispatch, control flow, and bindings should compose without changing semantics.
law: (= (if (do {setup} {cond}) (< {a} {b}) (>= {a} {b})) (if {cond} (< {a} {b}) (>= {a} {b})))
